skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Listen to bees related news. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.

Everything here is designed for beginning, sideline and commercial beekeepers who want the latest information on keeping bees.

#SaveTheBees
